    public interface CanHoldContext
    An additional interface that can be implemented by the HasAssignmentContext class. The assignment context holder (see AssignmentContextHolder) can than use this interface to store assignment contexts directly on the HasAssignmentContext class, if the assignment permits it (the Assignment.getIndex() is implemented, i.e., a non negative index is returned).
